    },
    {
      "global_id": 5887,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 3,
      "verse_key": "84:3",
      "text_ar": "وَإِذَا ٱلْأَرْضُ مُدَّتْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And when the earth is spread out"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5888,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 4,
      "verse_key": "84:4",
      "text_ar": "وَأَلْقَتْ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And hath cast out all that was in her, and is empty"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5889,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 5,
      "verse_key": "84:5",
      "text_ar": "وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتْ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And attentive to her Lord in fear!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5890,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 6,
      "verse_key": "84:6",
      "text_ar": "يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ إِنَّكَ كَادِحٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ كَدْحًا فَمُلَـٰقِيهِ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Thou, verily, O man, art working toward thy Lord a work which thou wilt meet (in His presence)."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5891,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 7,
      "verse_key": "84:7",
      "text_ar": "فَأَمَّا مَنْ أُوتِىَ كِتَـٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Then whoso is given his account in his right hand"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5892,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 8,
      "verse_key": "84:8",
      "text_ar": "فَسَوْفَ يُحَاسَبُ حِسَابًا يَسِيرًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "He truly will receive an easy reckoning"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5893,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 9,
      "verse_key": "84:9",
      "text_ar": "وَيَنقَلِبُ إِلَىٰٓ أَهْلِهِۦ مَسْرُورًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And will return unto his folk in joy."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5894,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 10,
      "verse_key": "84:10",
      "text_ar": "وَأَمَّا مَنْ أُوتِىَ كِتَـٰبَهُۥ وَرَآءَ ظَهْرِهِۦ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "But whoso is given his account behind his back,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5895,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 11,
      "verse_key": "84:11",
      "text_ar": "فَسَوْفَ يَدْعُوا۟ ثُبُورًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "He surely will invoke destruction"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5896,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 12,
      "verse_key": "84:12",
      "text_ar": "وَيَصْلَىٰ سَعِيرًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And be thrown to scorching fire."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5897,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 13,
      "verse_key": "84:13",
      "text_ar": "إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ فِىٓ أَهْلِهِۦ مَسْرُورًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "He verily lived joyous with his folk,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5898,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 14,
      "verse_key": "84:14",
      "text_ar": "إِنَّهُۥ ظَنَّ أَن لَّن يَحُورَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "He verily deemed that he would never return (unto Allah)."
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5899,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 15,
      "verse_key": "84:15",
      "text_ar": "بَلَىٰٓ إِنَّ رَبَّهُۥ كَانَ بِهِۦ بَصِيرًا",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Nay, but lo! his Lord is ever looking on him!"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5900,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 16,
      "verse_key": "84:16",
      "text_ar": "فَلَآ أُقْسِمُ بِٱلشَّفَقِ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "Oh, I swear by the afterglow of sunset,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5901,
      "surah": 84,
      "ayah": 17,
      "verse_key": "84:17",
      "text_ar": "وَٱلَّيْلِ وَمَا وَسَقَ",
      "text_en_pickthall": "And by the night and all that it enshroudeth,"
    },
    {
      "global_id": 5902,
      "surah": 84,
